- Perplexity mode to use (Pro Search/Labs/Deep Research)
- Model selection (Claude 4.5 Sonnet recommended)
- Any prerequisite information gathering needed

**3.2 Step-by-Step Usage**
1. [First action with specific details]
2. [Second action with specific details]
3. [Continuation steps...]

**3.3 Customization Points**
- List of all [CUSTOMIZE] sections with guidance on what to enter
- Examples for common scenarios
