**Section 4: Best Practices**
- Do's: [List of recommended approaches]
- Don'ts: [List of things to avoid]
- Optimization tips for better results
- When to iterate vs. when to start fresh

**Section 5: Troubleshooting**
| Problem | Possible Cause | Solution |
|---------|---------------|----------|
| [Common issue 1] | [Why it happens] | [How to fix] |
