</documentation_requirements>

<formatting_preferences>
- Use clear headings and subheadings (H2, H3 structure)
- Include a table of contents with page/section links
- Use tables for comparison information
- Use bullet points for lists
- Include code blocks or formatted sections for the actual prompt
- Professional but accessible tone
- Suitable for both personal reference and sharing with colleagues
</formatting_preferences>

Please generate this documentation in a format that can be easily exported to PDF or shared as a reference guide.


Usage Notes: Use this in Labs mode. The output will be formatted as a professional document you can save, export, or add to your prompt library.
